e wejdą w roku 2018.' => 'The user management module, called the People Register application, is one of the base parts of the application. It is in this module that most of the features that the application contains are referenced. The module allows, among others. Import / export user lists from and to systems with .xls or .xlsx extensions, or other formats such as .csv, files that are compatible with programs such as Microsoft Excel or Open Office. The formula for how to look at the table for importing workers is provided in the documentation to the system. Of course, you can add / edit / delete users (Employees) and their data in the system. Functionality has been prepared so that the system can start working as quickly as possible with a minimal amount of input. However, if you take more time to enter relevant information, the program will help you on many issues. Starting with the employment register with the option to find employment status on a given day, along with the documents that were in force on that day. And ending with the register of key permissions or alarm codes. Listen to what I can do: assign roles to employees; Assign employees to groups so you can map the entire organizational structure; Empower workers to the premises; Give advanced permissions to the Cryptos system; Modify permissions for personal data files; Assign to the user care about the collection of personal data; Add permissions to systems / registers; Keep your employment history and attach files; Keep a record of the employee`s expressed consent. In addition, I allow you to keep a register of electronic signatures with their authorized persons and a register of bank accounts along with the persons authorized to carry them. I also allow you to add permissions to additional systems and maintain a registry of changes for a particular person. You probably noticed that some of these features are the preparation to fill the RODO obstructions.I am ready for the changes that will come in 201